    • EntityEventHandler

      protected EntityEventHandler(int id, int dispatcherCount, LiveScoutFeedListener listener, LiveScoutFeed feed)
      Initializes a new instance of the EntityEventHandler class
      Parameters:
      id - The id of the current EntityEventHandler used to determine which messages will be processed by the current instance.
      dispatcherCount - The number of EntityEventHandler instances handling user events
      listener - The LiveScoutFeedListener instance used to inform the user about incoming messages
      feed - The LiveScoutFeed which will be passed to method calls on the user provided listener
